			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Flooding">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Mental health">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="2. What are the top hazards, disasters, and threats of concern that your community may face in the future?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Flooding">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Heat">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Mental health">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="3. What are the key equity concerns you identified in the data?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Some neighborhoods experience more flooding than others">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Some communities do not have access to needed information to adequately prepare for emergencies">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Workshop activities">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="4. What were the top concerns that community members expressed through storytelling and the results from future scenarios discussion?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
