			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Mental health">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="6. What are the key assets that support resilience in your community that were identified in the mapping?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Neighborhood community centers can distribute supplies and information">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Indicator Assessment and equity discussion">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="7. What indicators were the least resilient and least equitable? Which of these should be priorities for action?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- There is a lot of flooding in certain neighborhoods that causes repeated damage.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="8. What indicators were the most resilient and equitable, and why? What can be replicated or learned from for potential actions?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="area">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="For example:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Prompt"
			text="&#xD;- Most households have broadband access because of a grant recieved by the county and targeted outreach through social service programs.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock type="block">
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="9. What are key systemic or structural issue affecting equity that should be addressed through action in the next section?">
